      <a target="_blank" href="mailto:?body=https%3A%2F%2Fthewalrus.ca%2Fthe-vaccine-problem%2F" rel="noopener"><img alt="Share via Email" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/social-icons-email.jpg" /></a></div>
</div>
</div>
